      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23796430&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=5422&rangeEnd=5488",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/72732010716b1ace727c0f1?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=5422&rangeEnd=5488"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23796430_38_9964-10054",
      "chapterUid": 38,
      "range": "9964-10054",
      "markText": "瑞妮嘴里说出来的姑娘或女人都是迟钝的，身上却有许多可让人攫抓之处，就像个攀缘构架。她会被神奇地剥夺了尖叫或动弹的能力。她会束手无策，不知所措——因为震惊、愤怒或羞耻。她会孤立无援。",
      "totalCount": 162,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23796430&chapterUid=38&rangeStart=9964&rangeEnd=10054",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/72732010716b1ace727c0f1?chapterUid=38&rangeStart=9964&rangeEnd=10054"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23796430_6_5907-5925",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "5907-5925",
      "markText": "树上小小的绿苹果像眸子般望着她远去。",
      "totalCount": 156,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23796430&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=5907&rangeEnd=5925",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/72732010716b1ace727c0f1?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=5907&rangeEnd=5925"
