    {
      "bookmarkId": "23796430_12_1152-1258",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "1152-1258",
      "markText": "说到喜欢，这可是两码事。喜欢需要时间。我没有时间来喜欢你。我无法集中精力去喜欢你。",
      "totalCount": 156,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23796430&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=1152&rangeEnd=1258",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/72732010716b1ace727c0f1?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=1152&rangeEnd=1258"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23796430_88_8006-8078",
      "chapterUid": 88,
      "range": "8006-8078",
      "markText": "“他太不谨慎了。考虑到理查德，他不该那样做。不过，他没有家人，而且，要知道，我们俩是情人——暗地里相爱很久了——再说，他还能指望别的什么人呢？”",
      "totalCount": 153,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23796430&chapterUid=88&rangeStart=8006&rangeEnd=8078",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/72732010716b1ace727c0f1?chapterUid=88&rangeStart=8006&rangeEnd=8078"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23796430_6_1970-2041",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1970-2041",
      "markText": "然而，她却感到他们俩是孤立的。他们头上的苹果树似乎不是树，而是一个帐篷；他们周围似乎有一条用粉笔画的界线。在这界线之内，别人是看不见他们俩的。",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23796430&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1970&rangeEnd=2041",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/72732010716b1ace727c0f1?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1970&rangeEnd=2041"
    },
    {
